instance twinning_time_scale : DTDFVocab:TimeScale [
    base:desc "Continuous real‑time data exchange between the physical building and its digital twin, enabling synchronization as soon as sensor or BIM updates become available. The system does not specify explicit polling intervals or latency thresholds, but the real‑time data exchange capabilities imply sub‑second to real‑time performance, ensuring that the virtual replica reflects the state of the physical asset with minimal delay."
